### Users list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### User by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Blogs list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/blogs?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Blog posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/blogs/1/posts?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Conversations for user (requires X-User-Id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/conversations?page=0&size=10
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Conversation detail (requires X-User-Id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/conversations/1?page=0&size=20
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Single message (requires X-User-Id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/conversations/1/messages/1
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Notifications (requires X-User-Id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?page=0&size=10
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Photos list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/photos?page=0&size=12
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Photo by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/photos/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Profiles list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profiles?page=0&size=10
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Profile by user id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profiles/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

